Notebook Documentation — Bias Detection Notebook
This document explains the structure and logic of bias_fairness_notebook.ipynb.
Sections
1. Data Setup — Load Adult dataset, define sensitive attributes.
2. Baseline Model — Train logistic regression.
3. Bias Detection — Compute Disparate Impact and SPD.
4. Mitigation — Apply Reweighing from AIF360.
5. Comparison — Compare fairness metrics and accuracy.
Key Libraries
• aif360
• scikit-learn
• pandas
• numpy
• matplotlib
Outputs
The notebook outputs fairness metrics and a comparison table to show improvements after mitigation.
